      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.25rem);font-weight:400;color:#191817;line-height:1.12;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
        Adjusting Your Auction Reserve Mid-Campaign in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(25,24,23,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The number you have in your head at the listing meeting is almost never the number you sign on the reserve form. Here is how the conversation evolves between week one and auction day, and when you should move.
      </p>
    </div>
